highlights.text: “Baila bailalaa” by Kinderen voor Kinderen is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Netherlands, up 81 spots at #82.
“Hier Mag Alles” by Donnie and Marco Schuitmaker has been on Top Songs Netherlands the longest, at 674 days straight.
Olivia Dean has the most spots on Top Songs Netherlands. “Man I Need” is the highest at #2.
“Altijd Voor Je Zijn” by Milo ter Reegen and René le Blanc is the highest new entry on Top Songs Netherlands at #98.
